#10000
A deserted hanger~
Your presence accompanies a deserted F-16 falcon sitting in the middle
of the hanger, draped in brown cloth torn by constant use. Shelves
hanging from black smoke-tainted hinges surround the walls of this
hanger. Danging light fixtures sway to the calling of the wind as
it rushes from the entrance to the rear of the hanger. The shadows
provide plenty of cover and can hide even the most visible people.
~
