#10001
A deserted hanger~
You stand at the rear of this deserted hanger. The large doors which
seem to be the exit of this hanger have long been blown off and all
that remains is reminents of a black powder surrounding the hanger
door frame. The exterior of the hanger contains many metal sheets
which covered the hanger at one time; floating and hanging from lack
of maintenance.
