#10002
A ruined runway~
The broken concrete makes you cautiously move along this destroyed
runway. Patches of concrete missing reveals that this runway was
bombed beyond any future use. The ground in and around the runway
is painted with black smoke and red dust. The skyline is engulfed
in a reddish fire color, suggesting the destruction was recent. All
that remains of this runway are strapes of concrete and broken grass.
~
