#10003
A ruined runway~
The runway makes a rough transition from broken concrete to smoldering
grass and dirt. The black smoke emitted from the grass consumes the
landscape and hinders the details of the landscape in the distance. A
haze seems to sway with the wind as it passes back and forth from your
position. A large parimeter fence stands tall in front of you, blocking
any passage to the north.
