#10004
A large control tower~
Towering in front of your position lies a broken control tower. Large
bulks of wiring and probes hang from a large hole blown into the
tower recently. Small electrical sparks emit from the hole, suggesting
some power source still running nearby. The camoflauge paint of the
tower has been reduced to patches of blackened ash and smoke. A small
entrance, big enough for you to enter, lies in the rubble of the tower.
~
