#10005
Inside the control tower~
Squirming through the rocks and metal of the blown hole. You manage to
enter into the base of the control tower. Overturned tables containing
electrical consoles flood the room along with scrapes of metal, mounts
of ash, and a cloud of smoke. A small fire still burns along the lower
rim of a barrel labled, "Flammable Substance". A large metal stairway
lies above you, the upper half destroyed and hanging on some scrap metal.
~
