#10006
Inside the control tower~
The eastern wall of the tower remains, although weakened from the blasts,
it prevents any from continuing to the east. Along the eastern wall of
the control tower lies many footlockers and man-size lockers, obviously
for personnel use only. Looking to the south you notice that the southern
wall has been completely destroyed and nothing remains but hanging wires
and pipes from the sides of the blasted area.
~
