A large control tower~
You stand infront of a destroyed control tower, the southern wall 
completely destroyed from an unknown blast. The smoldering grass 
which is now covered in metal and stone, releases small amounts of
fumes that suggest recent explosions. The walls around the blasted
area are caked with heavy amounts of ash and dust, probably from
kicked up dirt in the explosion. A small path leads to the south.
