#10008
A broken cobbled path~
The path contains many patches of dirt and concrete thrown into random
places from the destruction of this air-base. A large tail-end of a
plane stands embeded into the ground on your right. The ends bent and
molded into an unknown pattern. The large parimeter fence to your east
kills any suggestion of traveling in that direction. The broken path
continues to the south of your position.
