#10009
A large gas generator~
At the corner of the intersection of the southern and eastern fences
lies a large gas generator. Miraculously it still runs although choking
from the lack of fuel left in it. A piece of the metal which contains
the accual generator has been blown open and reveals some of the
mechanical parts of the running generator. You notice some small sparks
coming from inside the generator locating from two wires which seem to
have been severed from the blast.
~
