#10010
A large taxi runway~
You stand on a runway used to taxi aircraft from the main runway to
the hangers. A large deserted blackened hanger lies far to the west
of your position. This runway isnt too badly damage and could be
repaired if any personnel were left to repair it. The concrete here
contains small rocks and pebbles from thrown concrete as the blast
sent concrete flying across the runways.
