#10011
Entrance to deserted hanger~
The hanger sits with the ends running north to south. However a large
blown hole lies in the eastern wall of the hanger, making penetration
into the hanger easier from the east. Inside the hanger you see a large
rod which originates from an aircraft which has been intacted from the
destruction of the airfield. The concrete becomes dirt here as large
patches of destroyed runway run under your feet.
~
