#10012
A small dirt path~
Mounds of ammo and expended shells cover the dusty path leading from
the hanger to a small jeep lot in the distance. Footprints cover most
of the path in a random pattern from the hysteria of the attack on
the airfield. Gazing to your right you notice half of a skeleton lieing
on the ground. Bones either cracked or charred, the identification of
this person will never be revealed. The path continues to your east and
west.
~
