#10013
A military parking lot~
Overturned vehicles and automobiles cake the military lot here. All
appear to be undrivable and therefore considered useless. Some either
smoldering in small flames or leaking battery and engine fluids; others
with body damage that can never be repaired. The lot itself didnt
completely evade any destruction. Cracks in the concrete and even patches
of concrete missing appear to cover this parking lot, making repairs
a futile effort.
~
