#10014
A ruined runway~
The long strip of runway engulfs your small stature as you look
wildly to your east and west. The runway, now containing large
fragments of rock, dust, ash, and smoke, was in full use just minutes
before the attack began. Now reduced to rubble, the runway is only
a reminder of the destruction that occured just hours ago. This large
runway continues to run to the east and west of your position.
~
