#10015
An abandoned aircraft~
A large cargo carrying aircraft stands before you with its nose smashed
into the concrete. This aircraft, obviously destroyed during the attack,
was in position to takeoff before it was destroyed on the runway. The
scent of burning engine fuel surrounds you as you notice a small fire
burning where the gas tank use to be. All that remains is a large hole
in the port side of the aircraft, caused from a nearby explosion.
~
